  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research is to test a text message intervention for people who are
      beginning an attempt to quit smoking. The intervention seeks to teach people to think about
      their cravings to smoke in more helpful ways. The investigators expect that participants
      receiving the text message craving program will be less likely to begin smoking again
      compared to participants in a control condition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
